    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211750/extras/b18a84fa0b10129b36b19d5cd031e5db.poster.avif?t=1770205975\" width=650 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211750/extras/b18a84fa0b10129b36b19d5cd031e5db.webm?t=1770205975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211750/extras/b18a84fa0b10129b36b19d5cd031e5db.mp4?t=1770205975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《霓虹新城》（Neongarten）是一款引人入胜的回合制策略游戏，融合了战术深度与极简设计，灵感来自《岛民》和《幸运房东》。沉浸在充满活力、浸透霓虹光芒的世界中，每个回合都带来新的挑战和机遇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一个成长中数位花园的建筑师，你将精心放置结构和单位来扩展领地，在过程中获得资源并解锁强大的组合效应。风险与回报的平衡至关重要。你会选择稳妥行事，还是赌一把高风险的升级？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211750/extras/a4cced12b0b017f26ffd4e71f7d7b902.poster.avif?t=1770205975\" width=736 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211750/extras/a4cced12b0b017f26ffd4e71f7d7b902.webm?t=1770205975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211750/extras/a4cced12b0b017f26ffd4e71f7d7b902.mp4?t=1770205975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《霓虹新城》有着程序随机生成和策略深度的独特组合，让你必须时刻保持警觉。每局游戏都提供全新体验，要求你不断适应、优化并精进你的战术。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回合制策略：谨慎规划你的行动，每个决定都将塑造霓虹新城的未来。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序随机生成：每一局都独一无二，提供无尽的可重玩性和全新挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极简赛博朋克美学：沉浸在令人惊艳的复古未来世界中，闪烁的光芒与战略深度交相辉映。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受《岛民》和《幸运房东》启发：将城市建设的简约性与肉鸽类游戏的进阶刺激感结合起来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是想要轻松又引人入胜的策略体验，还是具有深度且不断变化的解谜游戏，《霓虹新城》都能为你提供这两种内容的独特融合。</p>",
